The paper deals with joint source and channel coding for wireless image transmission, which is a topic that falls under information theory (cs.IT) and computer vision (cs.CV). The use of convolutional neural networks (CNNs) also suggests that the paper could be relevant to multimedia (cs.MM) and machine learning (cs.NE, cs.LG).
